<br>
Hags have a single target dd that they use against you if your running, or out of melee range. They have an ae spell they use when your in melee range, it only hits for like mid 100's if i remember correctly.<br>
<br>
The key here is to close to melee and take her out quick, I'm pretty sure that she will only use the ae if you close to melee range, and once past her damage absorbtion shield she should drop fast.<br>
<br>
So close to melee range fast and take her out, I know this doesn't help the puller, but if you have one show up at your group location this should help.<br>
