<br>
At early 20s, your best bet is to run for the zone, hitting your TRAIN hotkey (/shout Choo Choo to zone ... run, gate, evac .... get out of the way!)  You won't be able to stick a cease/desist or bash (reliably) to interrupt those 200 pt DD spells coming at you.  <br>
<br>
When you are level 30, plot your revenge.  A good group can take them.  At 45, come back and destroy the basement.  Then do the same to those specs in Oasis that trashed your mid-teen toon.<br>
<br>
Eggolas Moria (45)<br>
